17:19.581 --> 17:26.151
So what we ought to do is evaluate our life and see what changes we need to make, right?

17:26.572 --> 17:28.915
Changes to make sure that we're on that right path.

17:29.336 --> 17:34.104
Changes is make sure that we are growing and doing what we need to do to grow.

17:34.825 --> 17:38.290
And I think the pandemic has given us a good chance

17:38.530 --> 17:45.396
to sit down and evaluate and think about our lives, giving us kind of a break from all the hustle and bustle and everything.

17:45.777 --> 17:56.247
So I'm gonna go through a few things here and talk about my own life a little bit to see, to inspire you guys to sit down and look at your life and see, do I need to make a change?

17:57.208 --> 17:59.009
Is what I'm doing right?

17:59.770 --> 18:04.234
Is what I'm doing, what a growing Christian should be, a growing, changing, evolving Christian?

18:04.975 --> 18:06.416
Let's look at a few things, the basics.

18:06.436 --> 18:08.178
We'll look at the very few basics, right?

18:08.258 --> 18:12.723
talking about prayer, like how consistent is your prayer life?

18:13.104 --> 18:14.065
