22:08.133 --> 22:11.216
So we've got to evaluate our lives and see where can we fit that in?

22:11.336 --> 22:13.778
Can we pray more?

22:15.298 --> 22:16.299
Let's look at the Word of God.

22:16.439 --> 22:17.821
