23:51.709 --> 23:53.872
Now, every day, I'm trying to do the checklist and reading it.

23:53.892 --> 23:54.793
So what did I start to do?

23:54.833 --> 23:55.895
Well, I was inspired by him.

23:55.935 --> 23:57.857
I said, oh, you know, I'm going to get the Bible app.

23:57.937 --> 23:59.139
Now I do it on my phone, right?

23:59.439 --> 24:00.320
I'm going to do the checklist.

24:00.340 --> 24:03.064
I'm going to do the check mark next to say that I did it every day.

24:03.124 --> 24:04.145
I read the Bible, right?

24:04.185 --> 24:05.447
I'm going to check it off on my list.

24:05.848 --> 24:06.989
