24:07.029 --> 24:10.193
What is it that's going to make you say, I want to learn more of the Bible.

24:10.634 --> 24:11.294
Study more.

24:11.815 --> 24:12.756
Check it off, right?

24:13.117 --> 24:15.620
Again, it's fundamental to know what his will is.

24:15.700 --> 24:17.202
If you want to be a growing Christian,

24:17.346 --> 24:19.589
You've got to know what he says in this book, right?

24:20.090 --> 24:23.194
If you don't know what he says in this book, you're lost, right?

24:23.494 --> 24:24.896
