24:25.417 --> 24:27.179
You're being ignorant, and we don't do that.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.602
Finally, last point, we'll evaluate.

24:29.622 --> 24:32.206
And of course, there's a lot more things you can look at when you look at our lives.

