25:15.682 --> 25:17.005
That never ends.

25:17.025 --> 25:19.431
There's never an excuse to not serve God.

25:19.571 --> 25:24.883
Are we living the life of cross the Christ even during the pandemic?

25:25.004 --> 25:26.427
Finding ways to serve.

