26:43.239 --> 26:44.340
You guys think about your life.

26:44.721 --> 26:54.610
How can I, even during this pandemic, do something, do something for God, to spread his word somehow, to do something,

26:54.690 --> 26:57.456
whatever it is, even it's in my own family, right?

26:57.997 --> 27:07.777
