29:13.591 --> 29:18.898
You all gonna say, yes, reading the Bible's good, yes, praying's good, yes, serving God is good.

29:19.618 --> 29:21.500
You guys will say that, that's your stated priority.

29:21.981 --> 29:32.774
But if you wanna be a growing Christian, a changing Christian, you've gotta examine your life today and say, hey, are my actual priorities in line with that?

29:33.074 --> 29:35.738
