29:49.186 --> 29:50.848
The answer is yes.

29:51.730 --> 29:52.130
Let's pray.

29:52.931 --> 29:54.373
Dear God, thank you for your word here.

29:54.974 --> 29:57.217
We Christians will see new creatures, right?

29:57.357 --> 29:59.200
New creatures, old things are passed away.

29:59.560 --> 30:01.723
Help us to be new creatures, God.

30:01.743 --> 30:09.895
Help us to know your word that as we live our lives, that more and more and more, we grow as Christians.

30:10.535 --> 30:14.841
That we can say in our lives that we're trying to do everything we can.

30:15.282 --> 30:18.226
No matter what situation, pandemic or no,

30:18.562 --> 30:24.268
to say that we are with you, God, and we are doing your will, God.

30:25.208 --> 30:26.430
God, we ask you to help us with this.

30:27.070 --> 30:27.871
Watch over us.

30:28.472 --> 30:29.913
Bless us the rest of this week.

30:30.293 --> 30:38.982
Lord, give us relief from this horrible pandemic that hopefully it'll become easier and easier for us to do those things which we know are right.

30:40.083 --> 30:44.167
Watch this congregation wherever we are that you'll bless us throughout this week.

30:44.187 --> 30:45.909
We pray these things in Jesus' name.

30:46.369 --> 30:47.410
Amen.

